<actions>
  <insert-node tree="identifier: LendingPoolLiquidationManager [2373,2402]" parent="contract_declaration [2364,20845]" at="0" />
  <insert-node tree="is: is [2403,2405]" parent="contract_declaration [2364,20845]" at="1" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.maxLiquidatableReserveFee > 0  && vars.userCollateralBalance >= vars.maxCollateralToLiquidate.add [8998,9100]" label="vars.maxLiquidatableReserveFee > 0  && vars.userCollateralBalance >= vars.maxCollateralToLiquidate.sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.userStableDebt.add(vars.userVariableDebt).percentMul [7520,7577]" label="vars.userStableDebt.sub(vars.userVariableDebt).percentMul" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.debtAssetPrice.mul(debtToCover).mul(10**vars.collateralDecimals).percentMul(vars.liquidationBonus).div [17212,17319]" label="vars.debtAssetPrice.mul(debtToCover).mul(10**vars.collateralDecimals).percentMul(vars.liquidationBonus).mul" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.availableLiquidityAfter == vars.availableLiquidityBefore.add [20090,20155]" label="vars.availableLiquidityAfter == vars.availableLiquidityBefore.sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.collateralPrice.mul [17321,17345]" label="vars.collateralPrice.add" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.collateralPrice.mul(collateralAmount).mul(10**vars.debtAssetDecimals).div(vars.debtAssetPrice.mul(10**vars.collateralDecimals)).percentDiv [17538,17681]" label="vars.collateralPrice.mul(collateralAmount).mul(10**vars.debtAssetDecimals).mul(vars.debtAssetPrice.add(10**vars.collateralDecimals)).percentDiv" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.actualDebtToLiquidate.sub [11056,11086]" label="vars.actualDebtToLiquidate.add" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.userCollateralBalance.sub [8879,8909]" label="vars.userCollateralBalance.add" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: vars.userCollateralBalance.sub(vars.maxCollateralToLiquidate).sub [9379,9444]" label="vars.userCollateralBalance.add(vars.maxCollateralToLiquidate).sub" />
  <delete-node tree="identifier: LendingPoolLiquidationManager [2373,2402]" />
  <delete-node tree="is: is [2403,2405]" />
</actions>
